          <text id="/tb_education/note_on_tb/important_note_on_tb:label">
            <value>Kumbuka kwamba ugonjwa wa TB si wa kurogwa au kurithi
Ugonjwa wa TB unatibika kwa dawa za hospitali</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/note_on_tb:label">
            <value>Tanbihi</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/prevent_tb_spread/prevent_tb_spread_note:label">
            <value>Njia ya kuzuia maambukizi:
Kikohozi salama
Kuepuka mikusanyiko ya watu wengi
Kukaa sehemu inayopitisha upepo wa kutosha
Kugundua wagonjwa na kuwatibu mapema</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/prevent_tb_spread:label">
            <value>Njia ya kuzuia maambukizi</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/note_to_chv:label">
            <value>&lt;span style="color:#f58a1f"&gt;Kwa CHW:- Uliza kama kuna swali.&lt;/.span&gt;</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/num_people_reached:jr:constraintMsg">
            <value>Idadi iwe baina ya 0 na 100</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/num_people_reached:label">
            <value>Kwa kikao hiki umewafikia watu wangapi uliowapa elimu ya TB?</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/num_people_with_tb:jr:constraintMsg">
            <value>Idadi iwe baina ya 0 na idadi ya watu waliofikiwa</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/num_people_with_tb:label">
            <value>Kwa kikao hiki ni wangapi wana dalili za TB?</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/people_reached_note_to_chv:label">
            <value>&lt;span style="display:block;color:red;font-style: italic;padding-left:1em"&gt;Usimsomee, jaza wewe (CHV). &lt;/span&gt;</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv/tb_symptoms_note_to_chv:label">
            <value>&lt;span style="display:block;color:red;font-style: italic;padding-left:1em"&gt;Usimsomee, jaza wewe (CHV). &lt;/span&gt;</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/question_for_chv:label">
            <value>Masuali kwa CHV</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/suggestion_for_chv/submit_form_note:label">
            <value>Tuma hii fomu ya elimu, alafu uendelee kuhudimia watu kwa huu mfumo upendavyo</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/suggestion_for_chv/take_sample_note:label">
            <value>Unapaswa kuchukua sampuli au kutoa rufaa. 
Tuma hii fomu ya Elimu, alafu ufungue fomu ya uchunguzi ya kila mtu ili umchuguze vilivyo</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/suggestion_for_chv:label">
            <value>Ushauri kwa CHV</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_causes/tb_causes_note:label">
            <value>Njia za maambukizi ni:
Unaambukizwa kwa hewa wakati mtu anakohoa, kupiga chafya, kuongea, kuimba, kucheka.</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_causes:label">
            <value>Njia za maambukizi</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_introduction/tb_intro:label">
            <value>TB ni janga ya kitaifa ambayo inaathiri dunia ikiwemo Tanzania. 
Huku Zanzibar wagonjwa wengi wa TB wanagundulikana kila mwaka.</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_introduction:label">
            <value>Utangulizi wa TB</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_meaning/tb_meaning_note:label">
            <value>TB ni nini? 
TB ni ugonjwa sugu wa kuambukizwa
Unasababishwa na vimelea wanaojulikana kama Mycobacterium Tuberculosis</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_meaning:label">
            <value>Maana ya TB</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_symptops/tb_symptoms_note:label">
            <value>Dalili za TB ni hizi: 
Kukohoa mfululizo kwa wiki mbili au zaidi
Kutoa makohozi yaliyochanganyika na damu, wiki mbili au zaidi
Kupata homa za jioni, wiki mbili au zaidi
Kupungua uzito au kukonda, wiki mbili au zaidi
Kutoka jasho jingi nyakati za usiku, wiki mbili au zaidi
Na dalili zinginezo

Mtu akiwa na dalili moja au zaidi kunauwezekano mkubwa ana TB</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/tb_symptops:label">
            <value>Dalili za TB</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/tb_education/types_of_tb/types_of_tb_note:label">
